<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1181.105663.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Conosiphon ianus Alvarez Fidalgo & van den Broek, sp. nov. Male (clear-winged form) in its natural habitat, El Parador (Roquetas de Mar), Almeria, Spain, 25 - XII- 2009. Photograph: F. Rodriguez Luque." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/915200" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1181.105663.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Graphic showing the flight period of Conosiphon ianus Alvarez Fidalgo & van den Broek, sp. nov., based on the 105 records gathered from collections and photographs. Graph: M. Alvarez Fidalgo." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/915209" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1181.105663.figure11>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Neighbour-Joining tree for Conosiphon ianus Alvarez Fidalgo & van den Broek, sp. nov., and related genera of the subfamily Asilinae. Laphria flava (Linnaeus, 1761) is used as an outgroup. Red indicates dark-winged males and blue indicates clear-winged males of C. ianus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/915210" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1181.105663.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Conosiphon ianus Alvarez Fidalgo & van den Broek, sp. nov., male holotype (MNCN _ Ent 344922) A habitus in dorsal view B habitus in lateral view Male paratype of the clear-winged form (PAFC) C wing. Male paratype of the dark-winged form (PAFC) D wing. Scale bars: 5 mm (A, B); 3 mm (C, D). Photographs: PAF." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/915201" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1181.105663.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Conosiphon ianus Alvarez Fidalgo & van den Broek, sp. nov., male terminalia A phallus in dorsal view B phallus in lateral view C right epandrium in dorsal view D right epandrium in lateral view E left gonocoxite and gonostylus in lateral view F hypandrium. Drawings: M. Trillo Camprodon." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/915202" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1181.105663.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Conosiphon ianus Alvarez Fidalgo & van den Broek, sp. nov. Female paratype (MNCN _ Ent 344924) A habitus in dorsal view B habitus in lateral view Female paratype from Aguadulce in PAFC C Ovipositor, dorsal view D ovipositor, lateral view. Scale bars: 5 mm (A, B); 1 mm (C, D). Photographs: PAF." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/915203" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1181.105663.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Conosiphon ianus Alvarez Fidalgo & van den Broek, sp. nov. Female in its natural habitat, Aguadulce (Roquetas de Mar), Almeria, Spain, 7 - XII- 2015. Photograph: PAF." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/915204" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1181.105663.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Conosiphon ianus Alvarez Fidalgo & van den Broek, sp. nov. Male (dark-winged form) in its natural habitat, Aguadulce (Roquetas de Mar), Almeria, Spain, 7 - XII- 2015. Photograph: PAF." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/915205" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1181.105663.figure7>
    dc:description "Figure 7. A holotype of Conosiphon pauper (Becker, 1907), male habitus in lateral view B syntype of Conosiphon similis Becker, 1923, female habitus in lateral view. Scale bars: 5 mm. Photographs: E. Wolff, courtesy of J. Pohl, ZMHB." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/915206" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1181.105663.figure8>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Four locations showing the habitat of Conosiphon ianus Alvarez Fidalgo & van den Broek, sp. nov. in the province of Almeria, Spain A type location in Cabo de Gata B aguadulce C vicar D almerimar. Photographs: F. Rodriguez Luque." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/915207" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1181.105663.figure9>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Distribution map of Conosiphon ianus Alvarez Fidalgo & van den Broek, sp. nov. in Spain, created from all available data, both collected specimens and published photographs. Map: M. Alvarez Fidalgo." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/915208" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

